title: The Strange Love of Martha Ivers (1946 film noir)
description:
<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0038988/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0038988/</a>

A 1946 film noir starring Barbara Stanwyck, Van Heflin, Kirk Douglas and Lisabeth Scott. Directed by Lewis Milestone. Music by Miklos Rozsa, maybe the best noir composer ever.

Great stars, great performances, and murder, amateur-style and with passion, exactly the way you or I would do it.
